            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is impressive in what it brings to the genre and I'm excited to further delve into the wilderness. However, it keeps similar pitfalls that were present in the early entries from decades ago. If you'd like to learn more about Pioneers of Olive Town, be sure to check back in with us by following us on Twitter ",
